WEBVTT

00:00:00.399 --> 00:00:02.510
Hey, good morning family, how are y'all

00:00:02.520 --> 00:00:06.309
doing today? Praise the Lord, it's me.

00:00:06.319 --> 00:00:08.190
I don't have my dynamic duo today;

00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:10.350
she's busy, but I'm going to go ahead and

00:00:10.360 --> 00:00:11.789
do this video with y'all because

00:00:11.799 --> 00:00:13.870
I'm running late. I hope I get

00:00:13.880 --> 00:00:16.670
this posted today, but if I don't, I'm

00:00:16.680 --> 00:00:19.189
sorry about that. I had family come in

00:00:19.189 --> 00:00:19.199
from

00:00:19.199 --> 00:00:21.310
out of town and they wanted to visit,

00:00:21.320 --> 00:00:25.390
so we visited with them.

00:00:25.400 --> 00:00:27.070
But I've got to get these videos out

00:00:27.080 --> 00:00:29.189
because the Lord has really put it on my

00:00:29.199 --> 00:00:31.749
heart to

00:00:31.759 --> 00:00:35.310
lead you all in prayer for

00:00:35.320 --> 00:00:38.709
what's coming. We see another ministry

00:00:38.719 --> 00:00:39.950
with another

00:00:39.960 --> 00:00:44.910
scandal; it's very sad the way it's going,

00:00:44.920 --> 00:00:47.830
and it grieved me a lot over

00:00:47.840 --> 00:00:50.510
the last day or two. My wife has been

00:00:50.520 --> 00:00:52.150
reading about it and telling me about it,

00:00:52.160 --> 00:00:54.670
and I warned you this was

00:00:54.680 --> 00:00:58.630
coming. I told you back in

00:00:58.630 --> 00:00:58.640
November of

00:00:58.640 --> 00:01:01.910
last year

00:01:01.920 --> 00:01:03.709
that the Lord told me there would

00:01:03.719 --> 00:01:05.870
be great ministries that would have

00:01:05.880 --> 00:01:08.350
things uncovered,

00:01:08.360 --> 00:01:09.630
scandals that would be

00:01:09.640 --> 00:01:12.270
uncovered, and that He would

00:01:12.280 --> 00:01:15.590
raise up new faces, new generals in

00:01:15.600 --> 00:01:17.670
the army. There would be a

00:01:17.680 --> 00:01:19.749
cleaning of the house, as judgment

00:01:19.749 --> 00:01:19.759
begins

00:01:19.759 --> 00:01:22.149
in the house of the Lord first. We

00:01:22.159 --> 00:01:25.630
see that happening a lot this year. This

00:01:25.640 --> 00:01:27.710
year has been exactly what He said it would

00:01:27.720 --> 00:01:29.550
be, and I believe we're going to see more

00:01:29.560 --> 00:01:31.469
to come: major churches and major

00:01:31.479 --> 00:01:33.550
ministries that have tried to hide

00:01:33.560 --> 00:01:36.590
things

00:01:36.600 --> 00:01:38.350
they didn't want

00:01:38.350 --> 00:01:38.360
anyone

00:01:38.360 --> 00:01:40.270
knowing about. They tried to

00:01:40.280 --> 00:01:44.630
sweep it underneath the rug. Sadly,

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:47.069
we're all human and we all mess up.

00:01:47.079 --> 00:01:50.149
When our lives

00:01:50.149 --> 00:01:50.159
are

00:01:50.159 --> 00:01:53.590
on display, it's easier for others to judge

00:01:53.590 --> 00:01:53.600
and

00:01:53.600 --> 00:01:55.550
point fingers

00:01:58.640 --> 00:02:00.990
because these leaders have such a platform and

00:02:01.000 --> 00:02:05.310
influence in the world. So we

00:02:05.320 --> 00:02:07.789
just show grace; that's what we do.

00:02:07.799 --> 00:02:09.790
Yeah, it hurts the body of

00:02:09.800 --> 00:02:13.110
Christ, but we just keep standing.

00:02:13.120 --> 00:02:15.910
No matter who we see fall

00:02:15.920 --> 00:02:19.670
around us, no matter

00:02:19.670 --> 00:02:19.680
how

00:02:19.680 --> 00:02:22.070
shocked

00:02:22.070 --> 00:02:22.080
we

00:02:22.080 --> 00:02:25.110
are,

00:02:25.120 --> 00:02:26.910
it's going to happen more and more

00:02:26.920 --> 00:02:28.910
because the

00:02:28.920 --> 00:02:33.550
body of Christ went to a

00:02:33.560 --> 00:02:34.550
seeker-friendly

00:02:34.560 --> 00:02:37.869
message, not a holiness and fire

00:02:37.879 --> 00:02:40.830
message. Walking with the fire

00:02:40.830 --> 00:02:40.840
and

00:02:40.840 --> 00:02:43.470
the glory is what

00:02:43.480 --> 00:02:45.869
changes you; we go from

00:02:45.879 --> 00:02:48.990
glory to glory to glory. But when we

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:51.949
put up a hand to the Holy Spirit and

00:02:51.959 --> 00:02:54.990
don't allow Him to change us

00:02:55.000 --> 00:02:56.830
because of pride,

00:02:56.840 --> 00:02:59.229
money, or influence

00:02:59.229 --> 00:02:59.239
from

00:02:59.239 --> 00:03:01.750
social media

00:03:03.760 --> 00:03:06.990
awards,

00:03:06.990 --> 00:03:07.000
we

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:10.390
get a big head in ministry.

00:03:10.400 --> 00:03:12.630
A lot of times it's like what the Lord spoke

00:03:12.640 --> 00:03:17.070
to Diana when He said, 'You

00:03:17.080 --> 00:03:18.830
were so used to coming to Me

00:03:18.840 --> 00:03:21.430
for a word every

00:03:21.440 --> 00:03:23.949
day, and then all of a sudden you

00:03:23.959 --> 00:03:25.869
automatically assume what I'm going

00:03:25.879 --> 00:03:29.070
to say.'I paraphrase,

00:03:29.080 --> 00:03:31.750
but you

00:03:31.760 --> 00:03:34.630
see a lot of ministries

00:03:34.640 --> 00:03:37.509
that no longer feel

00:03:37.519 --> 00:03:39.670
they have to have that fresh fire every

00:03:39.680 --> 00:03:42.390
day because they're running on

00:03:42.400 --> 00:03:44.030
fumes.

00:03:44.040 --> 00:03:47.429
It allows the enemy to

00:03:47.439 --> 00:03:51.030
find an inroad to distract and

00:03:51.040 --> 00:03:55.190
destroy you. So first and foremost, you

00:03:55.200 --> 00:03:59.110
always have to have your guard up with

00:03:59.120 --> 00:04:02.030
the blood, communion, and seeking Him.

00:04:03.560 --> 00:04:05.470
I don't know these people personally,

00:04:05.470 --> 00:04:05.480
but

00:04:05.480 --> 00:04:08.350
the Lord said to me,

00:04:08.360 --> 00:04:11.470
'Don't go on certain platforms.

00:04:16.880 --> 00:04:19.229
I want you to be separate unto

00:04:19.239 --> 00:04:21.390
Me for a season because I'm cleaning

00:04:21.400 --> 00:04:24.550
house for

00:04:24.550 --> 00:04:24.560
your ministry.'So

00:04:24.560 --> 00:04:26.950
I've

00:04:26.960 --> 00:04:29.710
just stayed to myself and I will

00:04:29.720 --> 00:04:31.710
continue to do so until the Lord

00:04:31.720 --> 00:04:33.990
releases me. He

00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:35.310
said, 'I want you right now to keep

00:04:35.320 --> 00:04:36.749
planting your roots and go

00:04:36.759 --> 00:04:39.430
deeper with

00:04:39.440 --> 00:04:41.790
Me. Enjoy

00:04:41.800 --> 00:04:44.790
life and find that place of happiness

00:04:56.080 --> 00:04:58.430
in everything you do—with your kids,

00:04:58.440 --> 00:05:00.070
your wife,

00:05:00.080 --> 00:05:02.749
your flowers,

00:05:02.759 --> 00:05:05.950
or your dog.'God is in everything and

00:05:05.960 --> 00:05:08.469
He made all

00:05:08.479 --> 00:05:11.670
things richly for you to enjoy.

00:05:11.670 --> 00:05:11.680
Ladies

00:05:11.680 --> 00:05:14.230
and gentlemen, I want you today to enjoy

00:05:14.240 --> 00:05:16.590
life and the Thanksgiving that's

00:05:16.600 --> 00:05:20.070
coming up in America.

00:05:20.080 --> 00:05:22.070
We get so distracted by

00:05:22.070 --> 00:05:22.080
the

00:05:22.080 --> 00:05:23.749
pressure

00:05:23.749 --> 00:05:23.759
of

00:05:23.759 --> 00:05:25.990
performance

00:05:25.990 --> 00:05:26.000
and

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:28.390
trying

00:05:28.400 --> 00:05:32.670
to succeed, but

00:05:32.680 --> 00:05:35.710
whenever

00:05:35.720 --> 00:05:38.510
the rubber meets the road and you

00:05:38.520 --> 00:05:40.790
are standing before the Father,

00:05:40.800 --> 00:05:43.150
there will be nothing there other

00:05:43.160 --> 00:05:44.309
than you and

00:05:44.319 --> 00:05:47.710
Him. If you spend your whole life

00:05:47.720 --> 00:05:49.510
trying to build your kingdom and not

00:05:49.520 --> 00:05:52.990
His, what matters most when you

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:54.790
take

00:05:54.800 --> 00:05:56.390
your last

00:05:56.400 --> 00:05:59.430
breath is

00:05:59.440 --> 00:06:01.150
your relationship with Jesus

00:06:01.150 --> 00:06:01.160
Christ—not

00:06:01.160 --> 00:06:03.270
how much money,

00:06:03.280 --> 00:06:05.390
cars, or

00:06:07.520 --> 00:06:09.230
jewelry

00:06:09.230 --> 00:06:09.240
you

00:06:09.240 --> 00:06:11.390
have.

00:06:11.400 --> 00:06:15.150
It's the relationship you had

00:06:15.160 --> 00:06:18.189
with Him from Monday

00:06:18.199 --> 00:06:19.790
through

00:06:19.800 --> 00:06:23.749
Sunday in the mundane when

00:06:23.759 --> 00:06:26.270
nobody else is looking—not behind a

00:06:26.280 --> 00:06:29.390
camera, not

00:06:29.390 --> 00:06:29.400
on

00:06:29.400 --> 00:06:32.950
Instagram or Facebook. That's all

00:06:32.960 --> 00:06:34.909
fake anyway. Most people are

00:06:34.909 --> 00:06:34.919
just

00:06:34.919 --> 00:06:37.629
posting a story, but their lives are falling apart. They put on

00:06:37.629 --> 00:06:37.639
a facade that everything's beautiful: 'Hashtag, I've

00:06:37.639 --> 00:06:39.670
got my piña colada in my hand

00:06:39.670 --> 00:06:39.680
and I'm resting on the beach,'but the

00:06:39.680 --> 00:06:41.390
life is falling apart

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:48.749
without

00:06:53.360 --> 00:06:55.589
the

00:07:00.080 --> 00:07:03.469
selfie. It's so self-absorbed.

00:07:03.479 --> 00:07:06.189
That's why I hate social media

00:07:06.189 --> 00:07:06.199
because

00:07:06.199 --> 00:07:09.550
it's so fake. You

00:07:09.560 --> 00:07:11.550
get a call from

00:07:11.550 --> 00:07:11.560
someone

00:07:11.560 --> 00:07:12.990
weeping

00:07:13.000 --> 00:07:14.749
who

00:07:14.759 --> 00:07:16.990
is

00:07:18.960 --> 00:07:21.749
ready to do themselves

00:07:21.749 --> 00:07:21.759
in,

00:07:21.759 --> 00:07:23.710
yet

00:07:23.710 --> 00:07:23.720
you

00:07:23.720 --> 00:07:25.869
just saw a

00:07:25.879 --> 00:07:27.749
hashtag saying everything was

00:07:29.909 --> 00:07:29.919
great.

00:07:31.599 --> 00:07:33.670
People just need to be

00:07:33.680 --> 00:07:37.070
real because they're hurting inside, and

00:07:37.080 --> 00:07:39.110
only

00:07:39.120 --> 00:07:40.589
the Lord Jesus Christ can

00:07:40.589 --> 00:07:40.599
fix that.

00:07:40.599 --> 00:07:42.830
No matter how much money

00:07:42.830 --> 00:07:42.840
or success you

00:07:42.840 --> 00:07:44.749
find,

00:07:44.749 --> 00:07:44.759
or

00:07:44.759 --> 00:07:46.550
even

00:07:46.550 --> 00:07:46.560
a

00:07:46.560 --> 00:07:48.629
good-looking

00:07:48.629 --> 00:07:48.639
spouse—she's

00:07:48.639 --> 00:07:51.230
a 10 out

00:07:51.230 --> 00:07:51.240
of

00:07:51.240 --> 00:07:54.869
10 but she has issues,

00:07:54.869 --> 00:07:54.879
or

00:07:54.879 --> 00:07:57.390
he's a 10 out of 10 but

00:07:57.400 --> 00:07:59.950
he's abusive—people

00:07:59.950 --> 00:07:59.960
are still

00:07:59.960 --> 00:08:01.670
looking for

00:08:01.670 --> 00:08:01.680
that perfect

00:08:01.680 --> 00:08:04.189
10.

00:08:44.839 --> 00:08:48.590
Where is

00:08:48.600 --> 00:08:50.949
your heart with the Father? When

00:08:50.959 --> 00:08:53.230
it all comes to the end,

00:09:02.640 --> 00:09:04.710
you're going to stand before Him

00:09:04.710 --> 00:09:04.720
butt-naked,

00:09:08.350 --> 00:09:08.360
basically—stripped

00:09:08.360 --> 00:09:09.630
of

00:09:09.640 --> 00:09:13.910
pride and ego.

00:09:13.910 --> 00:09:13.920
Will

00:09:13.920 --> 00:09:16.190
your works

00:09:16.200 --> 00:09:18.990
stand

00:09:19.000 --> 00:09:21.750
in the refiner's fire as pure

00:09:21.760 --> 00:09:23.750
gold, or will they

00:09:23.760 --> 00:09:25.069
burn up

00:09:25.069 --> 00:09:25.079
like

00:09:25.079 --> 00:09:27.990
stubble? Did you do things

00:09:27.990 --> 00:09:28.000
for

00:09:28.000 --> 00:09:30.069
attention,

00:09:30.069 --> 00:09:30.079
like

00:09:30.079 --> 00:09:34.190
hashtagging

00:09:34.190 --> 00:09:34.200
a

00:09:34.200 --> 00:09:35.230
five-dollar

00:09:35.230 --> 00:09:35.240
gift,

00:09:35.240 --> 00:09:37.949
or did you do

00:09:41.120 --> 00:09:42.710
it because Jesus told

00:09:44.399 --> 00:09:47.550
you

00:09:50.360 --> 00:09:53.069
to?

00:09:55.440 --> 00:09:57.110
You'll know their

00:09:57.120 --> 00:10:00.030
fruit by the tasting. You can see

00:10:01.880 --> 00:10:04.069
the fruit on the tree.

00:10:04.079 --> 00:10:05.750
As

00:10:05.760 --> 00:10:07.509
Joyce

00:10:07.509 --> 00:10:07.519
Meyer

00:10:07.519 --> 00:10:09.230
said,

00:10:16.720 --> 00:10:18.069
an

00:10:18.079 --> 00:10:19.670
apple tree doesn't have to scream

00:10:19.670 --> 00:10:19.680
that it's an apple tree;

00:10:19.680 --> 00:10:22.230
it just is what it

00:10:22.240 --> 00:10:23.790
is. I don't

00:10:23.790 --> 00:10:23.800
have to

00:10:23.800 --> 00:10:26.710
try

00:10:29.959 --> 00:10:33.230
to

00:10:33.240 --> 00:10:34.949
fake the Holy Ghost.

00:10:54.600 --> 00:10:57.230
You

00:10:57.240 --> 00:10:59.790
can't live off of yesterday's

00:10:59.800 --> 00:11:01.870
revelation

00:11:01.870 --> 00:11:01.880
or

00:11:01.880 --> 00:11:04.670
anointing;

00:11:04.680 --> 00:11:07.110
you have to have a

00:11:07.120 --> 00:11:09.350
fresh touch every day.

00:11:14.440 --> 00:11:15.949
If you try to live off an

00:11:15.949 --> 00:11:15.959
old

00:11:15.959 --> 00:11:17.829
revelation,

00:11:27.200 --> 00:11:30.990
that water

00:11:32.079 --> 00:11:33.750
becomes

00:11:37.750 --> 00:11:37.760
stagnant.

00:11:45.760 --> 00:11:48.310
I want authentic with the Holy

00:11:48.320 --> 00:11:51.710
Spirit on a day-to-day basis.

00:11:56.839 --> 00:12:00.230
We try to

00:12:00.240 --> 00:12:03.790
bring what we have at home to you,

00:12:03.790 --> 00:12:03.800
but

00:12:03.800 --> 00:12:04.990
it's different

00:12:05.000 --> 00:12:07.069
through the camera when

00:12:08.639 --> 00:12:10.949
people

00:12:10.959 --> 00:12:12.509
judge you

00:12:12.509 --> 00:12:12.519
and

00:12:12.519 --> 00:12:15.470
don't know the Holy

00:12:15.480 --> 00:12:17.629
Spirit.

00:12:17.639 --> 00:12:19.030
You

00:12:19.040 --> 00:12:21.069
might

00:12:21.079 --> 00:12:23.069
have

00:12:23.079 --> 00:12:25.910
head

00:12:25.920 --> 00:12:27.430
knowledge

00:12:29.680 --> 00:12:31.949
from

00:12:33.760 --> 00:12:36.230
a

00:12:38.880 --> 00:12:40.829
sermon five

00:12:40.839 --> 00:12:43.110
years ago,

00:12:44.600 --> 00:12:46.509
but

00:12:56.680 --> 00:12:59.230
you

00:12:59.240 --> 00:13:01.910
don't know Him at all.

00:13:06.720 --> 00:13:08.629
I'm trying to help

00:13:08.639 --> 00:13:11.350
you fall in love with Him

00:13:11.360 --> 00:13:13.870
today.

00:13:17.440 --> 00:13:19.509
Do

00:13:21.839 --> 00:13:24.310
not

00:13:28.800 --> 00:13:30.389
put your

00:13:30.399 --> 00:13:34.230
relationship in somebody on TV or

00:13:34.240 --> 00:13:36.629
YouTube,

00:13:41.760 --> 00:13:45.389
because we're all human and we all have

00:13:45.399 --> 00:13:46.829
issues.

00:13:59.360 --> 00:14:01.710
I'm a work in progress. My

00:14:01.720 --> 00:14:03.230
wife tells me all the time, 'We're a work

00:14:03.240 --> 00:14:06.269
in progress, Brandon.'We

00:14:06.269 --> 00:14:06.279
may

00:14:06.279 --> 00:14:09.069
fall or stub

00:14:09.079 --> 00:14:10.629
our knee,

00:14:10.639 --> 00:14:12.550
but we pick

00:14:12.550 --> 00:14:12.560
ourselves

00:14:12.560 --> 00:14:14.710
back up like a

00:14:14.710 --> 00:14:14.720
beanbag

00:14:14.720 --> 00:14:16.230
clown

00:14:16.230 --> 00:14:16.240
that's

00:14:16.240 --> 00:14:18.269
standing on the

00:14:18.279 --> 00:14:21.150
inside.

00:14:21.160 --> 00:14:23.230
Are

00:14:23.240 --> 00:14:24.710
you

00:14:24.720 --> 00:14:27.430
standing on the

00:14:27.440 --> 00:14:30.470
inside?

00:14:30.480 --> 00:14:32.470
That's all that matters—not what

00:14:32.480 --> 00:14:35.470
your pastor

00:14:38.839 --> 00:14:41.749
or

00:14:45.040 --> 00:14:47.110
outside family

00:14:53.399 --> 00:14:55.269
says.

00:15:03.759 --> 00:15:05.590
Sometimes you have to cut yourself

00:15:05.600 --> 00:15:07.550
off from those who

00:15:07.550 --> 00:15:07.560
have

00:15:07.560 --> 00:15:09.509
a

00:15:09.509 --> 00:15:09.519
strong

00:15:09.519 --> 00:15:11.110
influence

00:15:11.110 --> 00:15:11.120
but

00:15:11.120 --> 00:15:12.870
try

00:15:12.870 --> 00:15:12.880
to

00:15:12.880 --> 00:15:14.269
lead

00:15:14.269 --> 00:15:14.279
you

00:15:14.279 --> 00:15:16.550
in

00:15:16.550 --> 00:15:16.560
another

00:15:16.560 --> 00:15:19.430
direction.

00:15:38.440 --> 00:15:40.749
It's

00:15:40.759 --> 00:15:43.470
time to shake off those

00:15:43.480 --> 00:15:45.949
beggar clothes like blind Bartimaeus on the

00:15:45.959 --> 00:15:47.430
side of the road.

00:15:57.720 --> 00:16:01.069
When he took off that cloak and gave everything to Jesus, he

00:16:01.079 --> 00:16:04.189
stood up and received his sight.

00:16:08.880 --> 00:16:13.030
Are you

00:16:24.800 --> 00:16:27.710
spiritually

00:16:27.720 --> 00:16:31.230
blind,

00:16:31.230 --> 00:16:31.240
